/DA (\057Helv 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg)
/DV (Purpose\072 This policy defines approved\054 prohibited\054 and controlled use of AI tools at the company\056\012\012Approved use\072 low\055risk drafting\054 summarization of approved materials\054 productivity support\054 generic templates\054 and approved coding assistance in sanctioned environments\056\012\012Prohibited use\072 entering PHI\054 payment data\054 credentials\054 secrets\054 private keys\054 customer confidential data\054 regulated records\054 or unapproved source code into unsanctioned AI tools\073 using AI for final high\055impact decisions without required review\073 deceptive\054 discriminatory\054 or unlawful content generation\056\012\012Employee responsibilities\072 use only approved tools\054 validate outputs\054 protect company and customer data\054 complete training\054 and report incidents promptly\056\012\012Vendor and tool rules\072 only approved AI tools with documented security\054 privacy\054 retention\054 and contractual review may be used for company business\056\012\012Monitoring and enforcement\072 the company may monitor AI usage through technical and administrative controls\073 violations may result in disciplinary action\054 access revocation\054 or legal escalation\056)
